museum which moved to washington with the hugheses in 1983 the 
independent taxexempt museum gets most of its financial support 
from membership dues souvenir sales and a grant from a potato 
research center in lima peru 
for 20 a year members receive six issues of the museums 
newsletter peelings and invitations to occasional potluck 
