intervened and stopped the effort to get goldens telephone records 
hartford and peluso declined requests for interviews to comment 
on the reports 
renzis son and the 400aday consultant who was renzis aide 
left the betac payroll early in 1988 according to pentagon sources 
the work betac does for the government is aboveboard theres 
been no wrongdoing by betac and this is all water over the 
dam said joseph royal the companys director of personnel 
